WEBVTT

00:00:06.791 --> 00:00:08.526
Are you sleeping restlessly,

00:00:08.526 --> 00:00:10.299
feeling irritable or moody,

00:00:10.299 --> 00:00:11.839
forgetting little things,

00:00:11.839 --> 00:00:14.602
and feeling overwhelmed and isolated?

00:00:14.602 --> 00:00:16.567
Don't worry. We've all been there.

00:00:16.567 --> 00:00:18.779
You're probably just stressed out.

00:00:18.779 --> 00:00:20.967
Stress isn't always a bad thing.

00:00:20.967 --> 00:00:24.178
It can be handy for a burst of extra
energy and focus,

00:00:24.178 --> 00:00:26.589
like when you're playing 
a competitive sport,

00:00:26.589 --> 00:00:28.516
or have to speak in public.

